---
import { FadeIn } from "./react/FadeIn";
import { Play } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      
      {/* Video Placeholder */}
      <FadeIn client:visible direction="right">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ana-text/5 group cursor-pointer shadow-2xl shadow-ana-terracotta-suave/10 border border-ana-terracotta-suave/10 transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.01]">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-ana-terracotta-suave text-white flex items-center justify-center pl-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
              <Play className="size-6 fill-white" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 text-center">
            <span class="font-inter text-sm text-ana-text/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-1 rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm">
              Vídeo de Apresentação
            </span>
          </div>
          {/* Placeholder Background - Replace with thumbnail later */}
          <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-ana-beige to-ana-offwhite"></div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

      {/* Content */}
      <FadeIn client:visible direction="left">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center h-full">
          <h2 class="font-playfair text-4xl md:text-5xl text-ana-text mb-8 leading-tight">
            Por que a <span class="italic text-ana-terracotta-suave">psicanálise?</span>
          </h2>
          
          <div class="font-inter text-ana-text/90 text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6">
            <p>
              Trabalho com esse método de tratamento por entender que não há respostas prontas para nossa vida.
            </p>
            <p>
              Cada um vive da forma que faz mais sentido para si. Meu trabalho é te auxiliar a encontrar seu caminho.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-ana-terracotta-suave/20 w-full">
            <h3 class="font-playfair text-2xl text-ana-text mb-4">Público</h3>
            <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-ana-beige rounded-full text-ana-text font-inter text-base font-medium border border-ana-terracotta-suave/20 shadow-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 cursor-default">Adultos</span>
                <span class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-ana-beige rounded-full text-ana-text font-inter text-base font-medium border border-ana-terracotta-suave/20 shadow-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 cursor-default">Adolescentes</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
